@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!
@appId = 1234567890
@versionFrom = 100
@versionTo = 200

# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{ "username": "{{username}}", "password": "{{password}}" }

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 设计态：版本 diff
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/apps/{{appId}}/versions/{{versionFrom}}/diff/{{versionTo}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 设计态：rollback 到指定版本
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/apps/{{appId}}/versions/{{versionFrom}}/rollback
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{ "note": "回退到上一个稳定版本" }

### 资源引用反查
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/resources/workflow/1234567890/references
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### FAQ：检索
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/faq?keyword=workflow&pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### FAQ：upsert
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/faq
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "title": "如何在画布上跨页面粘贴组件？",
  "body": "选中目标组件，使用 Ctrl+C 复制；切换到目标页面后 Ctrl+V 粘贴。",
  "tags": "canvas,clipboard"
}

### FAQ：命中（计数 + 1）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lowcode/faq/100/hit
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
